rating_comment: I had a wonderful stay at this apartment! The place was nicely furnished and incredibly comfortable, making it easy to feel at home. Its great location allowed for convenient access to local attractions. Mr. Rummon, the host, was exceptional—friendly, communicative, and very supportive throughout my stay. Highly recommend this place to anyone looking for a pleasant and hassle-free experience!
